## Welcome to Jessica Kent's Portfolio
#Resume 

Jessica Kent
Home Address: 27 ***********************	Telephone: (607) ***-****
Email: kentj09@mounties.mansfield.edu	Portfolio of work: https://github.com/kentj09 


SUMMARY
An effective leader, ready to find many different opportunities to gain knowledge. I have experience with multiple Microsoft applications, as well as some programming languages. I always strive to make sure that work is completed, and done in an effective manner. I am always looking for different challenges to accomplish. I am very dedicated to getting a task done, and going above and beyond the expectations set. I am extremely organized, to ensure that every task assigned gets done in a timely schedule. I am interested in multiple different areas in the computer industry, and I am always willing to take on a challenge. 


EDUCATION
Mansfield University of Pennsylvania	2013 - 2017
Bachelor of Science, Computer & Information Science (IS Track), 3.20 GPA

AWARDS, ACTIVITIES, and HONORS
•	Computer Science Club 2015-2017


EXPERIENCE
McDonald’s – Mansfield, PA	2011 – Present
GENERAL MANAGER
Experienced Restaurant Manager who oversees a high-volume, $2,200,000-million-dollar store. I am responsible for building sales, hiring new employees, tracking inventory, and creating a friendly environment for our customers as well as my employees. 

Millerton Wesleyan Church – Millerton, PA	2009 - Present
SOUND BOARD VOLUNTEER 
At Millerton Wesleyan I am very active in participating in the Worship Team. I work with various audio, and video programs to ensure an efficient and effective church service. I am responsible for starting up the sound booth equipment, and running the slideshows that the Pastor prepares each Sunday for his messages. I also am responsible for playing the music from the sound booth when necessary, as well as controlling the mics that are used during the service.   

REFERENCES
Upon Request.





### Skills
Java,SQL,Microsoft Word, Microsoft Ppt, Excel, Visual Studio, NetBeans IDE,Linux.


### About 
I am a student at Mansfield University currently in my senior year studying CIS.
